s are supposed to play inside this and the play area within these boundaries would remain the focus of our sports activities.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ed8e6ba elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ed8e6ba\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What will you learn from this webinar?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b5cad54 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b5cad54\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li>Why Ideal Customer Profile (ICP)<\/li><li style=\"font-size: 18px;\">What does ICP mean &amp; what does it address<\/li><li>Why now &amp; why is ICP gaining focus so quickly<\/li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight );\">Insight into ICP &amp; Buyer Persona<\/span><\/li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight );\">Examples of creating an ICP<\/span><\/li><li>ICP application<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-990dfbb elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"990dfbb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Speaker:<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/di